{"tid":820210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹逐漸增強，入黎講低遺言","createTime":"2018-09-15T09:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T10:35:34.000Z","uid":86695,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"06027ffe9196e454b3223199decae5e9bcd48f88","tid":820210,"uid":86695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"天文台講到好似好勁咁，香港就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f11e18747d50a67b21f408dd639961f7d60ea8a","tid":820210,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"我愛樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08237b5c741e1db7959c8e8ecf6c3ef64b7bb06","tid":820210,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:41:48.000Z","msg":"輕度颱風山竹<br />\n輕度颱風山竹為太平洋颱風季第十個被命名的風暴。「山竹」一名由泰國提供，是一種水果。此名字為第一次使用，替代在2006年嚴重影響菲律賓及越南，由於造成了廣泛的破壞而被除名的颱風榴槤。"},{"pid":"eb249ec42401acecceb8fc2a47ed8e5074441e8c","tid":820210,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"怕閪咩 我而家就出去滑水 屌你老母"},{"pid":"e3b19697fc54845e0cfcdd1eeea368794ad9acb6","tid":820210,"uid":141879,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"我想番工，唔想死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9244e6027e7ee6f9af292770ac58bf3709fb77e9","tid":820210,"uid":104387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06027ffe9196e454b3223199decae5e9bcd48f88","tid":820210,"uid":86695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"天文台講到好似好勁咁，香港就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"幾時有準過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873cfbb7035f7cd5e937828de5bc8f1d86f3b2cb","tid":820210,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20