g":"停電停水就大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4017882de1c7d1e3fdee547db0de66e6c428c7d","tid":820210,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"562391b531678be7504cecf683b7f7ab20e43521","tid":820210,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:48:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180914/58681885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F58681885&d=bWgaZwBvmeazD3cCoRUlqRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=60dd29b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180914%2F58681885&h=1597c6e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180914/58681885</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"天文台預測中心風力達12級颶風程度的超強颱風「山竹」將於周日（16日）進一步靠近香港，不少市民已四出搜刮膠紙、食物和飲用水預防風災。中電今日發出新聞稿，指山竹吹襲期間，供電網絡有機會受惡劣天氣影響引致電壓驟降、供電不穩、甚至停電，呼籲市民若在發現戶外電線斷落或電線杆倒冧，切勿觸摸或試圖移走，以免觸電，應立刻致電中電24小時緊急服務熱線匯報。<br />\n<br />\n中電稱，會密切監察山竹可能對供電系統造成的影響，並盡可能維持可靠供電，在風暴期間若遇上停電，客戶可致電熱線求助；若出現廣泛地區停電，中電將優先復電予需要電力儀器維持生命的客戶，以及醫院、鐵路、機場、廣播及電訊機構等公共機構。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5497eaedf538ad6584117dbb0339f92a31f540a","tid":820210,"uid":86695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:25:03.000Z","msg":"我愛連登"},{"pid":"ac51a1f81a8d06edea5a77918ddf4b4196f38908","tid":820210,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec34fe51080a74e002e86fd8fdf4a6fb962ad781","tid":820210,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:3